    "story": "You, a Foreigner in Japan, are preparing for a date in Shinjuku station. You need to navigate the bustling station to collect 3 random items for your date. You are excited but also a bit nervous about the adventure that lies ahead.",
    "description_scene": "You stand at the entrance of Shinjuku station, surrounded by the bright lights and the constant flow of people. The station is bustling with energy, and you can see people rushing to catch their trains or meeting up with friends. Signs in Japanese characters point in different directions, leading to various shops and platforms.",
    "options": {
        "1": "Head towards the shops to collect the first item on your list",
        "2": "Ask a station staff for directions to the lockers to put away your baggage before starting the search",
        "3": "Look for a map of the station to plan your route to collect the items",
        "4": "Take a moment to observe your surroundings and try to spot any familiar landmarks"
    }
}

