    "phase": 2,
    "story": "You decide to look for a map of the station to plan your route to collect the items for your date. You spot a station map not far from where you are standing, and you study it carefully to figure out your next move.",
    "description_scene": "The station map is displayed on a large signboard, with colorful markings indicating different shops, platforms, and facilities within Shinjuku station. As you scan the map, you notice the locations of shops selling various items that could be on your list. You also see symbols for lockers, bathrooms, and other amenities.",
    "options": {
        "1": "Head towards the shops to collect the first item on your list",
